spec_data.Name: python2-numpydoc
spec_data.Description:
Numpydoc inserts a hook into Sphinx's autodoc that converts docstrings
following the NumPy/SciPy format to a form palatable to Sphinx.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Tue 15 Aug 2017 12:44:10 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Sphinx extension to support docstrings in NumPy format
